		<a href="/topic/cxo/" class="topic">CXO</a>
	</p>
	<h1 class="title">How open climate data can improve community resilience against climate change</h1>
	<p class="byline">
					By <a href="/search/?a=alex+howard" class="author" rel="author">Alex Howard</a>
						<span class="date">March 25, 2014, 10:18 PM PST</span>
							<span class="separator">//</span> <a href="https://twitter.com/intent/user?screen_name=digiphile"><span class="icon-twitter-bird"></span> digiphile</a>
						</p>
	<div class="social-links">
