                            <h3>About <span itemprop="author">Alex Howard</span></h3>
                                                                        <p>Alex Howard writes about how shifts in technology are changing government and society. A former fellow at Harvard and Columbia, he is the founder of "E Pluribus Unum," a blog focused on open government and technology.</p>
