  </header><section class="fyre-comment-body"><div class="fyre-comment">
      <p></p><p>@digiphile @adornoe </p><p>A better read, than your Disinformation:</p><p><a href="http://factsnotfantasy.blogspot.ca/2014/03/a-history-of-disastrous-global-warming.html?m=0" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">http://factsnotfantasy.blogspot.ca/2014/03/a-history-of-disastrous-global-warming.html?m=0</a></p>
